reviewText: It is a really good breaking video even though you can tell that full force got robbed but with 70 crews battling there is some good battles in there.
I got this DVD for my sister who loves it! Very pleased b/c she's a tough critic.

This is crazy good footage and will definitely inspire you. It definitely inspired me. Once I saw this one it made me want to learn HOW they do that. the best instructional videos I found are How To Do The Robot - Breakdance Instructional DVD or Top 20 Breakdance Moves. So get this one for inspiration and then get those to learn HOW to do it!

I just recently received this dvd as a gift, and i gotta honestly say, this is one of the most hypes break videos i've ever seen.  I own many, seen tons, and as far as battles go, this video is top-notch.  I definitly recommend it to anyone who ever appreciated real bboys throwing it down.
this has to be one of my favortie bboy videos. battles are pretty hype. on disc 2 you can watch Rocksteady Crew get SMOKED by Havikoro! THIS IS A MUST GET!
